Geometric (Einstein): The source is any energy and mass. They literally "press" the fabric of spacetime. Imagine a tight trampoline with a weight on it. The weight is the mass, and the curvature of the trampoline is gravity. In this model, gravity is not a force, but a property of the shape of the universe itself.
